{"tid":592930,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"學生攜大提琴被帶走扣查惹爭議 港鐵稱當事人終獲放行","createTime":"2018-03-14T15:13:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-14T15:47:58.000Z","uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"394c30be23d1537af4d48e07903409f3f3f6173e","tid":592930,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T15:13:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180313/_2018031312253942833_detail.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180313%2F_2018031312253942833_detail.jpg&h=748cc44b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n港鐵在2015年推出「較大型樂器及體育用品計劃許可證」，所有乘客若要攜帶較大型樂器進入港鐵時，職員有權要求當事人提供證明。不過昨午有網民在太古站發現一名攜帶大提琴的學生被職員扣查，他因未能提供許可證被要求離開車廂，怒斥職員「小朋友都唔放過」，吸納近2000名嬲嬲，要求港鐵回應事件。港鐵其後主動回應指，職員最後已將學生放行。<br />\n網民Timothy Ho昨午途經太古站，見到一名學生被港鐵職員扣查，於是拍照片放到「巴打絲打Facebook Club」群組，斥「一個細路仔，就咁比人扣查，重聽到港鐵職員叫佢問老師點解比人扣留！小朋友都唔放過。」<br />\n帖文隨即被轉載至不同平台，不少網民認同Timothy的說法，批評港鐵職員「最叻咪選擇性執法」，「對個學生洗唔洗咁呀， 解釋完比人走啦。」<br />\n港鐵在其社交專頁主動回應事件，指太古站職員昨午收到乘客的來電，於是職員到列車了解，並要求學生到大堂的客務中心量度樂器盒尺寸。學生的樂器盒有一邊超出規定所限，而學生表示正在申請較大型樂器許可證，於是職員最後放行他。<br />\n但網民似乎不太接受回應，斥港鐵職員的做法不公「話有人投訴就去了解，咁平時我地投訴個D（啲）人帶大件行李，你地又唔處理」，「咩大型樂器許可證？一個學生著住校服拎住果咁嘅盒你有咩要懷疑」認為港鐵令所有事件變得複雜，最後只會令前線職員受苦。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/662035-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E6%94%9C%E5%A4%A7%E6%8F%90%E7%90%B4%E8%A2%AB%E5%B8%B6%E8%B5%B0%E6%89%A3%E6%9F%A5%E6%83%B9%E7%88%AD%E8%AD%B0+%E6%B8%AF%E9%90%B5%E7%A8%B1%E7%95%B6%E4%BA%8B%E4%BA%BA%E7%B5%82%E7%8D%B2%E6%94%BE%E8%A1%8C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F662035-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF-%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E6%2594%259C%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%258F%2590%25E7%2590%25B4%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%25B8%25B6%25E8%25B5%25B0%25E6%2589%25A3%25E6%259F%25A5%25E6%2583%25B9%25E7%2588%25AD%25E8%25AD%25B0%2B%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%2590%25B5%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E7%2595%25B6%25E4%25BA%258B%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%25B5%2582%25E7%258D%25B2%25E6%2594%25BE%25E8%25A1%258C&d=tGUmkzaQjrZs4McMo98rltU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=9a873b89\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F662035-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF-%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E6%2594%259C%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%258F%2590%25E7%2590%25B4%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%25B8%25B6%25E8%25B5%25B0%25E6%2589%25A3%25E6%259F%25A5%25E6%2583%25B9%25E7%2588%25AD%25E8%25AD%25B0%2B%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%2590%25B5%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E7%2595%25B6%25E4%25BA%258B%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%25B5%2582%25E7%258D%25B2%25E6%2594%25BE%25E8%25A1%258C&h=433dc221\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/662035-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E6%94%9C%E5%A4%A7%E6%8F%90%E7%90%B4%E8%A2%AB%E5%B8%B6%E8%B5%B0%E6%89%A3%E6%9F%A5%E6%83%B9%E7%88%AD%E8%AD%B0+%E6%B8%AF%E9%90%B5%E7%A8%B1%E7%95%B6%E4%BA%8B%E4%BA%BA%E7%B5%82%E7%8D%B2%E6%94%BE%E8%A1%8C</a>"},{"pid":"1e898ceb4dfe26678adacc45269a05a0a69cce7a","tid":592930,"uid":75870,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T15:17:34.000Z","msg":"個證其實有咩意義"},{"pid":"07c20db243d72ee6b73475556fdb353638c5c3e7","tid":592930,"uid":156422,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T15:38:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4d37b28f1cdde22e6e864c94db21a94ce0f9174d","tid":592930,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"07c20db243d72ee6b73475556fdb353638c5c3e7","tid":592930,"uid":156422,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T15:38:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T15:47:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}